    <p><a target="_blank" href="https://get.uber.com/">Uber</a> and <a target="_blank" href="https://cabify.com/en">Cabify</a> are by far the best options to get around in the city, 
    including going from/to the airport. A ride from the airport can go from $12 to $30 regardless of the number of people in the ride. 
    A ride in the city can go from $2 to $9 depending on the distance and the time of the day. Download both apps while you still have phone service, 
    because they may send you a text to your phone for verification purposes. Check the rates of both apps any time you want to get a ride. 
    If you decide to rent a car for the day, the Zen Hotel Panama includes free parking for their guests!</p>
